Cardiff 13; Sheffield 13, Fife 3. Division 1 - Billingham 6, Medway 9;
Blackburn 11, Bracknell 4; Chelmsford 1, Guildford 6; Murrayfield 2, Manchester
6; Telford 6, Swindon 7.
